Format&gml. &gml.LAYOUT.
:exmp
:I2 refid='gtlayou' pg=major.gtlayou
:pc.This tag starts a layout section.
The layout tag is a special &WGML. tag used to
modify the default layout of the output document.
More than one layout section may be present, but all
layout sections must appear before the :hp2.&gml.gdoc:ehp2. tag.
The :hp2.&gml.elayout:ehp2. tag terminates a layout section.
See :HDREF refid='rflays'. for more information on the layout tag.
